Titanic Dataset Analysis This repository contains assignment work in the course of Artificial Intelligence CSC4101 for tabular data analysis. objectives:

Data manipulation
Handling null Values
Data analytics using bar plots
Pandas operations
Data preprocessing
Normalization & Standardization
HomeTask Notebook: https://colab.research.google.com/drive/13x6hRBpAlxmXCjJlFZvPJP83hfP3EWP2?usp=drive_link

Dataset: Titanic dataset from Kaggle Tools: Python, Pandas, Seaborn, metplotlib pyplot
